    "English": "A map showing the location of a nearby Autophage planetary settlement, acquired from an <span class=\"name name-special\">Autophage Synthesis Terminal</span>.<br><br>Select the map and use <VAL_ON>Plot Route (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> to pin the location in your Exosuit display.",
